<h2>The SEO Advantage for Corporate Sites</h2>
<p>Corporate websites have a structural advantage in SEO: they have more pages, more content, and typically more backlinks. But most Kenyan corporate sites squander this advantage with:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Slow load times from oversized images and unoptimised code</li>
  <li>Thin, generic service descriptions that Google ignores</li>
  <li>No local SEO setup (Google Business Profile, local schema)</li>
  <li>Missing metadata on internal pages</li>
</ul>
